HEADWORD: Whisket
<hw>Whis"ket</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf.
<er>Wisket</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>A basket; esp., a straw provender basket.</def>
<mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark> <rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Mach.)</fld> <def>A small lathe for turning wooden
pins.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 1648 -->⟦br⟧
